  m_text: "Welcome to the AEGIS-077 Instructional Slab\r\n\r\nYour task today is
    to repair the Boiler room control panel WIRING. \r\nPlease connect all wires
    node-to-node based on color. \r\n\nYou can place wires in all 4 cardinal directions
    of each slot, but wires of different colors CANNOT cross; so wire placement requires
    strategy.\r\n\nIf you select the wrong wire, click it again to deselect it, or
    right-click to delete undesired wires. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 17c56f7e47c154248a518b13dff16d6c, type: 2}
